2017-06-16T10:10:03.000Z","msg":"錢"},{"pid":"c4c878e0c8631b0eee3fb8765fa1780e71c9cf70","tid":285990,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:20:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有好多正正常常同自己差唔多既男仔唔揀<br />\n係要去揀中年老餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔識諗既, 俾MK仔扑.<br />\n識諗既, 俾阿叔扑.<br />\nMK仔分分鐘要養埋佢, 阿叔就算唔買LV都包你食飯買衫去旅行先啦.</blockquote><br />\n又唔好睇小mk仔銀包銀彈數量<br />\n都要睇mk仔 去開邊 去開lkf果堆 都有幾千銀落去玩轉 鬼仔多數幾舊水</blockquote><br />\n幾千<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個D就唔叫MK仔。個D就叫有錢仔，太子爺，二世祖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14cbc5da5f00e26c80ee9a6d7127e7db02bf0240","tid":285990,"uid":67087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:37:33.000Z","msg":"過來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為佢地多過同年紀既人好多人生經歷 <br />\n會覺得佢地好叻<br />\n同埋覺得自己咁後生簡佢 佢賺左喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n（佢地唔會咁諗 只會當你係g)<br />\n<br />\n屌 人地過人世點會搵你"},{"pid":"040ce51f23d6ff55bd72bf2fd9b135933fdf62bb","tid":285990,"uid":6136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:42:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">臭雞黎</span></span>"},{"pid":"7e5573cc41910186f0453d0f99d8eba551306d47","tid":285990,"uid":59961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:46:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌<br />\n以前返炒散<br />\n有個大波女有錢女 <br />\n雖然矮同講野on9<br />\n比個三十歲有老婆既部長屌</blockquote><br />\n部長比盡搵兩萬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a28d48c710adf80c364253d47af01e62a1ea5c","tid":285990,"uid":59961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:48:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為佢地多過同年紀既人好多人生經歷 <br />\n會覺得佢地好