90,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T13:02:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好簡單 同中年男人拍拖佢可以見到第二個世界<br />\n情況就等於你係小朋友果陣想成為大人一樣<br />\n20歲女同20歲仔拍拖<br />\n可能大家仲係食緊譚仔 返緊學 講學業<br />\n同35歲仔拍拖 可能你已經遊緊車河 品味生活 識投資賺錢 帶條女去唔同既場合餐廳 有事業<br />\n富二代都係一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n威"},{"pid":"99a25be23524a8eed56c99f1bc904dca5eafb60d","tid":285990,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T13:14:18.000Z","msg":"錢"},{"pid":"bd1fd66aeba161eab0a41f8e4e3cc64c029adeb2","tid":285990,"uid":26952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T13:25:41.000Z","msg":"識人50幾歲.中意同後生女拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢ex都係後生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}